headline: This Jabil Peer Reports Monday As AI Fever Boosts Top-10 Industry
summary: Many of the group's companies are reaping rewards from heavy spending in data centers, including group leader Jabil.  Fabrinet — which specializes in advanced electronics for tech companies — comes into its quarterly report with a tailwind from strong spending in cloud computing.  Analysts' consensus earnings estimate for Fabrinet is $2.43 a share, a 9.5% increase year over year.
